creator: Black Envelope
descriptionHtml:
Write your name in hieroglyphs!

This app translaterates from modern letters to the Old Egyptian hieroglyphs. Note that this app translates sounds of words, not necessarily meaning!

Transliteration is based on Manuel de Codage, the de facto standard for hieroglyph transliteration.
descriptionShort: Write your name in hieroglyphs! - Hieroglyphic transliteration from English

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Big UI and usability upgrade. Improved almost every aspect of the app. :)
